overview: Inari, Wendy, Amber, Jade and Kriztina have a few things in common and that's just a few videos under their belt, making them prime for Dirty Dirty #10. Jake Steed and Ed Powers give them the royal treatment. It may not be their first time, but it's their best! Enjoy!
tagline: There's Always A First In Every Box!
title: Dirty Dirty Debutantes 10
